{"tid":601330,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"藍罐曲奇真係好神奇，唔同時期會鍾意食唔同款","createTime":"2018-03-22T06:46:47.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-22T15:20:53.000Z","uid":3072,"like":22,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"ddf9bbe0e18ee9f895659110d2c42a7f17e2e7f0","tid":601330,"uid":3072,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T06:46:47.000Z","msg":"提子乾餅 &rarr; 純牛油餅 &rarr; 糖粉扭紋 ... 一路loop<br />\n<br />\n總之食厭一款又唔知點解開始鍾意另一款<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n明明樣樣都一樣味咁濟<br />\n<br />\n彩虹糖又唔會嫁喎，鍾意開檸檬味就永遠都係檸檬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5989795b6330ba20a5f71e8e87d03b3b40c3fda3","tid":601330,"uid":33733,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T07:16:13.000Z","msg":"一直最愛扭紋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8aaa013662610163c66ae012a715c03009f86019","tid":601330,"uid":176935,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T07:17:48.000Z","msg":"由頭到尾無變過<br />\n淨係食 純牛油 <br />\n正到hihi"},{"pid":"61254ebe288f5ec7b676d0bebd96b5c6c7f6dd98","tid":601330,"uid":152262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T07:18:38.000Z","msg":"乾子乾同圈圈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e21c5178113d6116dc8354a3b9b04e850a79022","tid":601330,"uid":152262,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T07:18:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span style=\"color: red;\">提</span>子乾同圈圈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"c07b1f1ebebb6b30c19cf13dd8bce0e0a3ce19ee","tid":601330,"uid":30804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T07:25:22.000Z","msg":"從來只愛牛油圈<br />\n以前其他味都會食下<br />\n而家冇牛油圈就索性唔食"},{"pid":"18638509f02f69580b0c5b2801f18640401d